node.text:
Live the ranch life without sacrificing modern luxuries. Sitting on ~140 acres of lush avocado groves, this ~17,000SF house has explosive views to the ocean & offers total privacy, sitting half way between Beverly Hills and Santa Barbara. Offered at $29,950,000 Represented by Jerome Kerr-Jarrett @kerrjarrettestates and Jeff Hyland @hyland_jeff
